{"tid":1670234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日唔會去撐加泰集會","createTime":"2019-10-23T02:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T05:44:42.000Z","uid":35430,"like":21,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fa8d45bd37200bcb2e99ebb44078ae888779a067","tid":1670234,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:33:48.000Z","msg":"講到明唔會去，但唔代表我會割蓆，我只係唔認同搞手做法唔睇風向，如果集會搞手背後唔係有共狗指點就係畀connect沖昏頭腦，麻煩你醒少少唔好破壞香港人呢四個月所付出嘅血汗同犧牲<br />\n無謂畀共狗有位入你正名港獨，我地係極需要美國人權法案通過"},{"pid":"43e5d1811838ad36032c28a19aa3133347df773a","tid":1670234,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:34:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef2dcbcee8e0ec582b51def3ebb340b88711f08","tid":1670234,"uid":201735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:34:24.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"e01133f32d0fb7ea0fc9c55fa9b7fbff448cdff5","tid":1670234,"uid":287594,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fa8d45bd37200bcb2e99ebb44078ae888779a067","tid":1670234,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:33:48.000Z","msg":"講到明唔會去，但唔代表我會割蓆，我只係唔認同搞手做法唔睇風向，如果集會搞手背後唔係有共狗指點就係畀connect沖昏頭腦，麻煩你醒少少唔好破壞香港人呢四個月所付出嘅血汗同犧牲<br />\n無謂畀共狗有位入你正名港獨，我地係極需要美國人權法案通過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:34:25.000Z","msg":"轉載：<br />\n<br />\n（點解一定要去加泰集會）<br />\n<br />\n1. 西班牙係民主國家，加泰係自治區<br />\n<br />\n2. 加泰隆尼亞獨立公投於2017年10月1日舉行，以決定加泰隆尼亞是否脫離西班牙而獨立。此次公投由加泰隆尼亞自治區政府發起，經加泰隆尼亞議會核准後舉行。獨立得票率達92.01%，獲議會認可。<br />\n<br />\n3. 西班牙政府則依據憲法法院判決認定此公投為非法，拒絕承認投票結果並監禁獨派領袖。<br />\n<br />\n（似曾相識？）<br />\n<br />\n=== === === === === === === === <br />\n<br />\n我好肯定獨立與否本身我地無需表態，因為加泰人民已經用合乎制度的公投形式表態。但「民主」政府無視合法公投民意、監禁社運領袖、警暴濫權我地理應身同感受。你唔出黎支持加泰，咁你一直以來究竟支持緊乜？<br />\n<br />\n（純屬個人意見：政治就係語言藝術，要spin 無論如何都spin到，要屌點都挑到骨頭。中共輿論控制爐火純青，五毛橫行。學懂保持獨立思考，會令我地更快步近民主。）<br />\n<br />\n同意請分享，好人一生平安。"},{"pid":"3d8d50c8c564161d7ab785fc59ef7e8e22406f2b","tid":1670234,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c60f9db33b10a9e64f73b2af96a467e5b15754f","tid":1670234,"uid":279321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:34:46.000Z","msg":"講完唔會割蓆之後即刻割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0db149d7d4ab5a1865b03e28583c3838dbac97","tid":1670234,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7f0da875108abf641596ecc4e0086350277783","tid":1670234,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/72768335_2473808126038251_6978876850143494144_n_ZiI2v_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F72768335_2473808126038251_6978876850143494144_n_ZiI2v_1200x0.jpg&h=63253f5d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11606c5f1ed9288b724f426ff038a5f0034b415e","tid":1670234,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:35:47.000Z","msg":"民族自決乃國際人權公約第一條第一句：<br />\nAll peoples have the right of self-determination.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我要聲援Catalonia。"},{"pid":"040e11c0115fe12cce2c51b90abf75fba0b191a4","tid":1670234,"uid":62133,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:36:07.000Z","msg":"原來想去<br />\n鍾意個理念<br />\n但既然大眾主流係唔去咁我都唔去<br />\n你唔割我我都唔割你"},{"pid":"4f67812befcc9ca16e6d7c3b40e22d59e9aa593f","tid":1670234,"uid":221360,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:36:39.000Z","msg":"去集會果班，唔代表全香港，就好似撐警集會咁，都唔係代表全香港。想去就去，唔想去咪唔好去，反而覺得大家post多d點解要支持／反對個集會既post，比大家自行決定會更加好。<br />\n最後，集會無可能影響我地既初衷，去既只係聲援佢地為自由所做既事，唔係聲援加獨。<br />\n<br />\n勿忘初心，方得始終<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n不自由，毋寧死。"},{"pid":"43b95f70929d581b6bf1d71a58258510aade3a7d","tid":1670234,"uid":106876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c60f9db33b10a9e64f73b2af96a467e5b15754f","tid":1670234,"uid":279321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:34:46.000Z","msg":"講完唔會割蓆之後即刻割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:37:36.000Z","msg":"似得你咩P牌仔 返去奶共啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f31970b2e197932518e1ed7709cddeb63594bd","tid":1670234,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:38:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔去加泰？<br />\n去英領！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【上議辯論造勢大會】<br />\n10月23日（三）<br />\n英國領事館門口<br />\n19：30<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y5iHJGT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy5iHJGT.jpg&h=30a60c49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"805d0a490ead4e1a4632b2511b5bf64a25d51caf","tid":1670234,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80f31970b2e197932518e1ed7709cddeb63594bd","tid":1670234,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:38:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔去加泰？<br />\n去英領！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【上議辯論造勢大會】<br />\n10月23日（三）<br />\n英國領事館門口<br />\n19：30<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.